# Pulumi stack config — regenerated from .env by the deploy runbook. Holds
# encrypted secrets + the encryption salt; kept out of git so nothing sensitive
# is committed even by accident. The base Pulumi.yaml and *.example stay tracked.
infra/pulumi/Pulumi.*.yaml
!infra/pulumi/Pulumi.*.yaml.example
